 drivers/net/ethernet/intel/ice/ice_lib.c     | 37 ++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/ethernet/intel/ice/ice_lib.h     |  2 +
 drivers/net/ethernet/intel/ice/ice_main.c    | 41 ++++++++------------
